</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Enomdar wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I just got the DPoC over the weekend and the focused Air pet still hits for a max of 85.  Have not summoned the other pets to text max melee.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
