			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Not really a bug with the mage class per se, but since the last patch (3/23), something is really funky with pathing and collisions:
<br />

<br />
*  As a gnome I get stuck going up very small stairs now (i.e. the ones leading to the "stones" cave in tranquility).  I'm used to hopping up some of the larger stairs, but the problem seems much worse with the new changes to the engine.
<br />
*  Navigating on a hill or up stairs with a horse or lizard is nearly impossible.  
<br />
*  Several people are falling under the world when up against a zone wall.  This is especially happening in corners.  
<br />

<br />
