				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">* Pets get "hung up" on corners in the scenery ("natural" or "artificial") when following, e.g.:
<br />
- Butcherblock, heading from the Adventurers' camp to the PoK book, by the turn to the north at the guard station
<br />
- Inside temples in GoD, in Ikkinz, in Tak
<br />

<br />
* Pets unable to path back to their master, especially in "indoor" zones that turn back on themsleves (e.g., Ikkinz, Tak)
<br />

<br />
* Pets unable to keep up with their masters with Run5 in indoor zones, barely able to catch up in outdoor zones. (59-62% from Velocity does not work indoors, and has been "obsoleted" by the prevelance of Run5.)<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
